snippet.title: Castlevania: Symphony of the Night Intro Story Trailer,
snippet.description:
Castlevania: Symphony of the Night was released in Japan, on the PS1 19 Years ago on this day, March 20th. To commemorate the occasion we put together a trailer for the cinematic opening story that was considered amazing at the time.

Happy 19th Anniversary Castlevania: Symphony of the Night !!!

Please Like & Subscribe.
